{"type": "article", "id": 28491, "title": "John Lewis 奢侈女装线不错，以及，一堆男装走秀值得一看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-21T07:36:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 1097, "name": "百货"}, {"id": 413, "name": "耳机"}, {"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 29223, "name": "品牌大使"}, {"id": 6582, "name": "春夏"}, {"id": 1618, "name": "赞助"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}, {"id": 21794, "name": "Beats by Dre"}, {"id": 21904, "name": "Piaget"}, {"id": 21593, "name": "Shinola"}, {"id": 29224, "name": "DFS"}, {"id": 331, "name": "John Lewis"}, {"id": 8084, "name": "Marni"}, {"id": 29225, "name": "德国国家队"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021613266FY92f1Bv40jDVRZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Ryan-Reynolds-becomes-Piaget-brand-ambassador,704943.html\"><b>Ryan Reynolds 成伯爵品牌大使</b></a>｜出演过“绿灯侠”的加拿大男演员 Ryan Reynolds ，近日开始担任瑞士奢侈腕表及珠宝品牌伯爵（Piaget ）的形象大使。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Shinola-hires-Tom-Lewand-as-CEO,705429.html\"><b>Tom Lewand 任 Shinola 公司 CEO</b></a>｜奢侈品旅游零售商 DFS 集团旗下的品质产品、腕表品牌 Shinola 上周宣布，Tom Lewand 将出任首席执政官。此前他为全国橄榄球联赛的底特律雄狮队效力 20 年，2009 年初从首席运营官升至总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Adidas-agrees-record-new-deal-with-German-soccer-team,705552.html\"><b>Adidas 继续赞助德国国家足球队</b></a>｜德国足协宣布与 Adidas 续约，后者对其的赞助合同将从 2018 年延长至 2020 年，每年提供 5000 万欧元（约合 5670 万美元）的赞助费用。此前曾一度传出 Nike 欲抢下这一赞助资格。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/20/11975758/gucci-diy-jackets-shoes\"><b>Gucci 拓展定制服务范围</b></a>｜五月，我们报道过 Gucci 开始提供酒神包的私人定制服务，可以选择刺绣图案、补丁和缝制首字母。而昨日 Gucci 在米兰发布了 2017 男装系列后，宣布可定制的产品扩展至男士衬衫、针织衫、皮夹克等，以及中性的棒球服、牛仔夹克和男女鞋。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161258sJZ8Ktz4m7hHoenL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161259LIeyWPog6p5aA3ck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">寻求更具质感的穿着？可以考虑英国<a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/john-lewis-luxury-range-modern-rarity-with-palmerharding-levi-palmer-matthew-harding-10459192/\"> John Lewis 百货首个自家奢侈女装产品线 Modern Rarity</a>，预计 9 月 8 日上市。由 John Lewis 采购部门总监 Jo Bennett 和设计部门总监 Iain Ewing 共同设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021612594LWYSTnG8hdsif1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161300XEFZrRPSnKxdGkfj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161301vxhHjMPFlf1JGOV6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613014l2OJmRYrLFqpbkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613024ltpcNU3PAr7TLkj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">日本设计师高桥盾创立的服装品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/undercover-beats-by-dre-powerbeats2\">UNDERCOVER 将与 Beats by Dre 推出合作款耳机</a>，预计七月中旬在 Apple 、连卡佛等店上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161302bVKwAMtHaPx8NXZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161303312T9zMVObGpUiYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161304gTaoQ952qDYprbwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161304Ika6HWB89Dsewv2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/milan/gucci/review/\">Gucci 发布 2017 春季男装</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161305Mr62auSntvAO8f95.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161307vL6OYM2F5VC73a0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161308CDpLVh8uISMgJfUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161309bYNUsXWGtoc4d0Ry.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161310HKIwc158NJpmx7DV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161311Ndi6DSJZxHrAGgQz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161312TnRYpctQh0omb9Z5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161312sdMqaXCzIEltj3FS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161313m9XD735BcxbAN8zM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">接着再来看看更成熟、“硬汉”风的<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/gallery/emporio-armani-mens-spring-10462042/#!83/emporio-armani-mens-spring-2017-95/\"> Emporio Armani 2017 春夏男装</a>： </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161313m3PuIsyWBkfJVrxL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161314kSwq0MfrzYn25psZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161315lNrDySJOVQ865ZW3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161315nJ602GIbaRmeUM3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161316F0Z4iSqXOUBJkA6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2017-menswear/marni\">Marni 的 2017 春季男装也不错</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613182uoApV7m0xFK9BgG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613213